reviewText: Great songs on here to sing along to. Alvin is funny as always. Great for kids.
my grandson really enjoys the video
I really have never opened this one. I was looking for another Alvin and the Chipmunks sing along. It has a lot of good songs and is, I'm sure, just as good as the other I purchased.
These HARD-TO-FIND tapes keep my special-needs child enthralled!  Simple and entertaining, even adults will want to watch & sing along!!  This is good old-fashioned entertainment!
